Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:07.10,Main,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi! Kanna! Breakfast is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This miso soup is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:16.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I made it using only \Ningredients from this world, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.90,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:23.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, watch out for cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:27.95,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, make you sure you don't \Ndestroy them if you run into one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:29.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:36.83,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! This morning I wasn't chastised \Nby Miss Kobayashi for any mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:39.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It was a perfect morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I must be improving my skills as maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps that means I'm getting \Nused to this world, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:29.14,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You've been happier lately, \Nhaven't you, Kobayashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:30.92,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:34.77,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be a bit more stoic before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:37.48,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you've become a little more open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sore ja}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:48.03,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's been two months \Nsince she showed up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:55.27,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,What was I like back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:01.35,Main-Top,Cook,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The secret is to marinate it in honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.74,sign_4304_21_Show_Logo,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,Today's {\c&H0000D7}Po{\c&H28D700&}i{\c&H00B1D7&}n{\c&HBFB60D&}t
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:04.66,Main-Top,Cook,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then it'll grow softer, and the\Nmeat will absorb flavor more easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:06.33,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Miss Kobayashi will eat my tail \Nmeat if I prepare it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:09.11,Main-Top,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What modern girls want \Ntheir lover to do most!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.50,sign_4511_25_2__Head_petted__,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,2) Pet their head \N{\3c&H1EB32A&}3) Hold their hand in public\N {\3c&H00B5CB&}4) Carry like a princess\N {\3c&H9D0B5F&}5) Hug them from behind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.29,Main-Top,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:14.08,sign_4568_27_2__Head_petted__,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,2) Head petted \N{\3c&H1EB32A&}3) Holding hands in public
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:14.08,sign_4584_28_1__Being_pushed_,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,1) Push them against a wall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.20,Main-Top,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}being pushed against a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:19.03,Main-Top,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd love to experience \Nit myself at least once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:18.68,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, so they pursue love with sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just like birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.13,Main-Top,Caster,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Pursue love...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:25.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.56,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now for tonight's news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:35.89,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Early this morning, there was a \Nfire in Tatsumi-cho, Nishi-ku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.07,sign_5231_39_Jigokumeguri_Sys,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Jigokumeguri System Engineering (Inc.)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.07,sign_5231_40_Takinokuchi_Offi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Takinokuchi Office
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:39.78,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:44.16,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you help me out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.51,Main,Kobayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.91,Main,Kobayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, you've taken on an awful lot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:56.74,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Miss Kobayashi \Nworking at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:02.42,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,One of my 48 maid skills:\Nperception blocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.22,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can enter without anyone noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.55,sign_5885_48_It_s_actually_ma,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,*It's actually magic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.85,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,There she is, there she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.28,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kobayashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.22,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Takiya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:25.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, remember Yamashita-kun's project?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:30.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There was a mistake in the product, \Nand he's in trouble if it's not fixed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:31.00,sign_6425_56_Yamashita_kun__O,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,181)}Yamashita-kun\N Out Sick
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.51,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.45,sign_6509_58_Sorry_,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:32.45,Main,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:35.71,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So for now, I'll work on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:40.12,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It means I won't be able to help you, \NTakiya-kun, but is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.67,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:42.58,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.29,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Especially given the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.09,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.01,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go drinking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.29,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:53.43,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you help me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.85,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there. Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.84,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,This schedule's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.07,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we adjust it somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.41,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We'll have to reevaluate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:07.79,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Humans may gather together, help each other,\N and accomplish many things,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.25,Main-Top,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:10.99,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,but their civilization could be \Neasily destroyed by dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:15.53,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,So I think dragons are better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.00,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.37,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,How's that project coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.37,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:24.44,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! You're useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.17,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.06,Main-Top,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I told you get it done right away, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.14,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:30.59,Main-Top,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,When I say right away, I mean right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.34,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Chief's pushing his work \Nonto Kobayashi-san again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:33.34,Main-Top,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Are you incapable of prioritizing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:36.45,Main-Top,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You need to work to earn your paycheck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:36.93,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,The chief's project isn't even that vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.29,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:41.19,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Quit slacking off and get \Nit finished quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:45.50,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.22,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.06,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Serves him right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:01.33,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That should help Miss Kobayashi—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.24,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.88,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was blocking perception?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:09.42,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,N-No one's found out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.66,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi sure works hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:34.51,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And so many people rely on her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:39.63,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:42.74,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:44.74,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,How's that project going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:47.13,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't received a report on it yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.13,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:50.60,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I had a lot of things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.99,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Follow my orders first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yamashita-kun's work \Nis higher on the priority list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:58.09,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:04.02,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.85,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Show more motivation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.24,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.93,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You're useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:13.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.75,Main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.16,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Chief's having bad luck today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.59,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.76,sign_10799_119_Jigokumeguri_Sys,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Jigokumeguri System Engineering (Inc.)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.76,sign_10799_120_Takinokuchi_Offi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Takinokuchi Office
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.60,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.76,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.81,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I should leave before \NMiss Kobayashi does...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:43.71,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:49.46,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, you really were?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:53.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.57,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a feeling you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.30,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.68,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it was boring to sneak \Na peek at my work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.71,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:11.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to know more about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:16.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:22.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:33.52,Italics,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You've been happier lately, \Nhaven't you, Kobayashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.40,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I used to be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.00,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I've already forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.28,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the chief got \Ncanned for abusing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:56.50,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Someone sent the director \Na recording of proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.63,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:08.33,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Now everyone pair up and please \Ndraw a picture of your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:16.44,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-san, would you draw me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.02,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.04,sign_13590_147_Episode_5,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 5
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.04,sign_13590_148_Tohru_s_Real_Wor,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru's Real World Lessons! (She Thinks She Understands It Already)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.55,sign_13644_149_Oborozuka_Shoppi,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Oborozuka Shopping District
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Asparagus, watercress, new potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:37.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I bought a bunch of vegetables in season!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:44.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Since we got them cheaper than planned, \NI guess I'll buy some snacks for Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:50.33,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fafnir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:55.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:59.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised to find you standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:03.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.87,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to live in \Nthis world for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:14.57,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I can't \Nrecommend it that strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.81,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Can you live with humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:20.20,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do it, then I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.76,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.72,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you stay he—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.96,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any place to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.54,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live in some nearby mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.72,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now for today's news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:37.49,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Last night there were reports of a \Nmonster spotted in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.74,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and police were dispatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:43.27,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The monster was said to \Nstand 20m at full height.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:44.77,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.20,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:50.38,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to sneak around \Nand hide from humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:54.31,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should just destroy them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forget about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:58.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be living amongst people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So you have to show some restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:04.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help search for a place \Nfor you to live, Mr. Fafnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:07.57,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:10.17,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you sure, Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.68,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:14.84,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave it to me, Mr. Fafnir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:18.42,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. I guess I'll see what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:24.27,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just the other day I watched Miss Kobayashi \Nmove out, so I understand the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.52,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:30.49,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You create a "family registration" \Nand a "proof of citizenship,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:34.70,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,also a "bank account" and a "personal seal," \Nthen you show them to a "realtor."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:36.04,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:40.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So, I made them for you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:43.53,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.32,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Is this me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.56,sign_16914_196_Ooyama_Takeshi,File,0000,0000,0000,,Ooyama Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:51.44,sign_16959_197__News_Thing,,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious Large Creature\N{\fs16\c&H00FFFF&}20 Meters Tall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:48.15,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:52.42,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,Your dragon form looked like \Nan Ooyama Takeshi, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.48,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You resemble them too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:59.42,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You're growing too close to humans now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:03.07,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,When you return to your world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:07.25,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,will you be able kill humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to return to my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:19.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:25.47,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,In a century or so, that human \Nyou're attached to will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.26,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:31.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:36.81,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The more I treasure these moments \Nand being here right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,the sadder I'll be when \Nthat time comes, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:46.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to call \Nthose feelings regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:51.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Green means go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:55.85,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You think they're worth \Nspeaking so highly of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:58.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Because Miss Kobayashi is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Were you worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:13.39,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I was just curious about what \Nhumans are like in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:18.69,sign_19023_219_Mitani_Real_Esta,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mitani Real Estate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:17.08,Main,Realtor,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it isn't Kobayashi-san's maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.42,Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.56,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.05,Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We're not a pawn shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:36.95,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, I'll steal a fittin—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:38.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, you won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:43.04,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there's no money exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:45.15,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Shows the limits of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:46.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:52.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it isn't best for \Nyou to live in your own world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:56.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's hard to live here \Nwithout a human you get along with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:05.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,There is a human you'd be \Nall right with, Mr. Fafnir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.82,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.71,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:13.07,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it isn't Fafnir-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:16.11,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you knew where I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:18.33,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mr. Takiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:21.36,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:27.61,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, would you let Mr. Fafnir \Nhere... stay with you for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.38,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Fafnir-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.91,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.60,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a little cramped, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.53,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You really mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:42.73,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm one to talk, but this \Ndragon's fairly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.60,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, about last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.60,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.19,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What others are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:52.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.52,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me more about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:15:02.46,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Was Mr. Fafnir really worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:10.46,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Now let's conduct the experiment \Naccording to the chart in your textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:12.10,Main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:15.64,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my text book. Show me yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.95,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.48,Main-Top,Magician,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now try bending it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:35.95,sign_22238_260_Super_powers___B,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,ESP! \NBending spoons
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:31.04,Main-Top,Magician,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't need to use any strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.72,Main-Top,Magician,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just bend it with your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:40.70,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't bend it with \Nstrength just now, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.71,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Incredible! How did it happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:43.45,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like he used magic either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:48.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, he did something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:51.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:54.30,flimsy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(66,56)}Bend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:55.47,flimsy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(66,56)}Bend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:56.76,flimsy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(66,56)}Bend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:57.56,flimsy - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(104,1)}Snap...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:58.31,flimsy,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(105,1)}Bend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.93,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.93,flimsy - Copy (2),,0000,0000,0000,,Hiss!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:03.18,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you've bent them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.84,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.42,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.69,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi! That! That!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.94,Main-Top,Magician,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now this 100 yen coin will \Npass through the cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.94,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's what you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:15.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is that rare? ESP?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.36,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,ESP?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:20.83,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So humans really do have hidden powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:28.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Miss Kobayashi wasn't \Njust an ordinary person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.12,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,God! Kobayashi God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.91,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.34,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,These are magic tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:36.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can do them once they learn how.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.81,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.95,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:45.36,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Humans usually only use about \N10% of their brain capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:50.37,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if humans put their minds to it,\N anyone would be able to use super powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:54.61,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to when they try. \NWhat crafty, lazy creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.14,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:56.98,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:59.31,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking something weird again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:03.45,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, this book was \Non Kobayashi's shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.46,sign_24464_294_You_Can_Do_It_To,Book,0000,0000,0000,,You Can Do It, Too! \NESP
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a book I bought long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:10.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So if you do this, \Nthen power enters your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.86,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's all fiction though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:17.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Training! This book provides good training!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.82,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going training!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.97,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru's easily influenced, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:25.23,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm free, so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll fix your spoons first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:29.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need ESP, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:36.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Again? How cliche.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.62,sign_25346_307_Training_1_Menta,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Training 1\NMental Fortification
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.96,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Will I actually learn how \Nto do it by doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.50,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you can do it, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:57.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Empty the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:01.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I have no desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:05.23,sign_25883_312_Training_2_Medit,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Training 2\NMeditation
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:03.45,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.21,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:10.70,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.20,sign_26304_318_Training_3__Clai,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Training 3\N Clairvoyance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.20,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.57,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi! Miss \NKobayashi! Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.95,sign_26415_322_Training_4__Thou,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Training 4\N Thoughtography
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.66,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Kobayashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's your horn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.92,sign_26620_325_Training_5__Form,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Training 5\N Forms
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.30,sign_26620_325_Training_5__Form,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Training 5\NForms
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:40.05,sign_26735_327_Training_6_Sparr,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Training 6\NSparring
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:45.75,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, please look! This is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:49.73,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Compilation: Bear Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.73,sign_27048_330_Training_Compila,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Training Compilation
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.73,sign_27048_331_Bear_Slayer,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Bear Slayer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.56,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to become?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:57.93,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:02.44,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:08.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You can do plenty of things humans can't,\N so isn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.68,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose to humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:16.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be inferior to them in any way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:20.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.50,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's like that, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:28.32,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I think you actually want \Nto understand humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:33.27,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,and that's why you're so desperate \Nto understand what you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.44,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:42.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You search for the spoon's center of gravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.78,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,then using the principle \Nof leverage here, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Once you understand, it's simple, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:20:01.86,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This is, at least. But there are \Nsome things that aren't that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:06.47,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tohru, you should focus on the \Nthings only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:21.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:37.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show you a \Npower only I can use!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:47.12,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But don't break anything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.21,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's not much I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.79,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the avatar of destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.55,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I can produce electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:00.91,sign_30136_362_Magic_Show__of_t,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Show \Nof the Century
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:21:00.91,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the beautiful lady has \Nentered the box. Please watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:03.83,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the super magic \Nof instant teleportation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:04.48,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.30,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, it's the moment of the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.61,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! Huh? Wha? A maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.71,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A maid has appeared from the box!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.41,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't what we planned? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:28.74,Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, give me a big helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.05,flimsy - Copy (3),,0000,0000,0000,,Milk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:31.14,Italics,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet and sour pork with pineapples?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:34.31,Italics,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:42.14,Italics,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:46.86,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,We're likely to have \Nleftovers, so here's extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:50.33,Italics,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,Extra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:28.01,sign_33687_377_Next_Episode,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,181)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:28.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, I learned new magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:29.67,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:31.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at this coin on a string.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:32.56,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:36.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You will fall deeper and deeper in \Nlove with Tohru! In love with Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:40.01,sign_33951_383_Episode_6,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Episode 6
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:40.01,sign_33951_384_Home_Visit___And,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Home Visit! (And Homes Not Visited)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.86,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's not magic.
